Hello, World! # Important: Be sure to set up the server-side implementation as per the instructions here, otherwise uploads will not work.
To get started, create a new HTML document. Download the script as per the &ldquo;Installation&rdquo; example, and include it in your head tag like so (remebering to replace the example path with the real path!):
&lt;script src=&quot;/path/to/dropzone.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
Include a &lt;form&gt; in your &lt;body&gt;:
&lt;form action=&quot;/file-upload&quot; class=&quot;dropzone&quot; id=&quot;my-awesome-dropzone&quot;&gt;&lt;/form&gt;
That&rsquo;s it!
